metadata.description: In a galaxy far, far away… not really, more like somewhere on planet earth coming from the minds of 2 Highly respected Street, Grafitti/Graphic Design Artists Ras Terms & Tusea Skywalker, you have the Star Bizarres. The Star Bizarre characters are blended with Sci-fi, pop culture, graffiti street art, East African Culture and world religions. Ras Terms has put in over 30 years creating his original Infamous bearded characters which can be seen all around the world. Combined with Tusea’s Street and Graphic design styles this is what shows up in the Metaverse.
metadata.name: Star Bizarre - Jyn Elektra
